page.title: 20The Children of W.C.P.S.
page.content:
In July 1985 there are 137 children at Wheelock County Primary School. This project is being done by the 7th year children who are 10 and 11 years old.
The children are:- Kevin Wain, Seth Thomas, Sarah Green, Louise Jane Twemlow, Rachael Brown, Kath Moore, Julie Wilson, Nigel Rolton, Samantha Taylor, Julie Brandreth, Catherine Banner, Joanne Buckley, Melanie Bebbington, James Ratcliffe, Andrew Smith, Carl Barber, Mark Cook, Paul Sandbach, Mark Bowers, Peter Livesey, John Appleton and Deborah Baker.
